04f2610207223ea8a8a2c8ade198014188b51398","tid":2001474,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T14:18:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/EAJM5L9hhBs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FEAJM5L9hhBs&d=QLsQNhMpkN58D9M0TNJg1lEyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=3a174a68\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/EAJM5L9hhBs</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T14:19:50.000Z","msg":"好重，著住好辛苦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T14:33:06.000Z","msg":"唔識physics 但起飛咗應該唔重？"},{"pid":"f113b38c83154f7b25ebffdf0cf14c94484e8d7b","tid":2001474,"uid":135693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T14:34:40.000Z","msg":"因為你無飛行號"},{"pid":"5d78c1b6c320bea23265bbc148295e3f34ce2e45","tid":2001474,"uid":339272,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T14:37:08.000Z","msg":"左腳踩右腳"},{"pid":"fd8b64726fad2f3b665337722be054beeeb39fe6","tid":2001474,"uid":15501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T14:39:23.000Z","msg":"你冇學舞空術？"},{"pid":"b6e928dd422c8c0279440f8fbc16f7efa9bf3db5","tid":2001474,"uid":297436,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T14:40:14.000Z","msg":"「識飛」同「好似雀仔咁飛」其實係兩個問題嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n或者話後者係前者其中一個複雜啲嘅做法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n某種意義上人類已經識飛 只係用另一種方式實現咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「好似雀仔咁飛」嘅飛機叫做Ornithopter<br />\n因為物理問題 所以直至現時都大唔得去邊 最多都係實驗載一個人<br />\n因為「拍翼」依個方式產生嘅升力同推力都唔係好足夠<br />\n<br />\n而「一個人用嘅飛機」就唔係做唔到嘅問題<br />\n而係唔實用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"644ff8847bb8fa2a746ccd29e8b9121e886432ed","tid":2001474,"uid":24615,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T14:45:01.000Z","msg":"你既意思係好似雀仔咁拍翼定點?<br />\n<br />\n係因為人造物料好難承受到拍翼呢個動作<br />\n以翼手龍黎計,200KG既重量差唔多要10米長既翼,仲要唔可以長時間拍翼,只係可以拍一陣滑翔一陣<br />\n<br />\n10米長200kg呢個係有機生物既極限咁制,人造出黎通常再差少少<br />\n<br />\n計番空間,成本,維修 成件事就冇晒商業價值"},{"pid":"03e934f398141dda5fb0d8db70d3819582aca7b6","tid":2001474,"uid":79442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T14:54:04.000Z","msg":"因為妳背脊骨受唔起多對翼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f9433d2904dcebb28dc9a47fe800ef2cc0cc291","tid":2001474,"uid":54524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb321aac8f8cd96b5b94253ae5f0fa2107607327","tid":2001474,"uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95b922e10d27a624e4a845d11b092b43033f02b0","tid":2001474,"uid":54524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3a8d79e348224103b5bacaf9db09e15dd3a3d5d9","tid":2001474,"uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T14:23:23.000Z","msg":"發明好似雀仔飛行嘅裝置"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T14:27:41.000Z","msg":"個個都識飛，航空公司咪執哂"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T14:29:26.000Z","msg":"冇衝突，飛得遠咪搭飛機，香港去新界就自己飛"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T15:10:17.000Z","msg":"咁點整空中邊境<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？可以隨便飛入人地國家咁點？"}]}